{"type": "article", "id": 30289, "title": "波纹表面的浴室家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-28T23:01:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160728222330IWiSAv7xgdGXKs9O.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://www.philippaduatz.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Philipp Aduatz</a> 最近为 <a href=\"http://www.klomfar.at/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Klomfar Vienna</a> 设计了一系列有着波纹表面的浴室家具，将它与所处环境最主要的自然元素结合在了一起。为了模拟出波浪的形态，Aduatz 不仅采用了 CAD 软件对结构进行渲染，还额外开发了一种新的制作技术消除不必要的接缝让家具一体成型。家具表面流畅的涟漪有一种像是透过水面窥见白色沙滩的感觉，有着以假乱真的视觉效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728223438jufd2n1Czr6tghPV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728223438HeOVi5P9F0GgdN8E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.787286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728223438lSCIvB9gb41XZasj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607282234388pwX9SE0VT2Bi3Nq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div>"}